hitokoto: In your life, some things are your best and do thebest, you will never want to give it up, for me, that is tennis. 在你的生命中，有些事情是你最擅长的，也做得最好的，你永远都不会想要放弃它，对我来说，那就是网球。
author: Roger Federer

hitokoto: No, Roger Federer doesn't put off, otherwise he doesn't wallk on the court. 罗杰·费德勒从不放弃，不然他就不会站在球场上。
